jasperReport.name: modelloC
jasperReport.queryString:
SELECT distinct o.name as ragioneSociale, o.banca as denominazione, coalesce( o.account_number, '' ) || ' · ' || coalesce( o.codice_impresa_interno, '' ) as codice, o.partita_iva as partitaIva, o.codice_fiscale as codiceFiscale, o.cf_correntista as codiceIstatPrinc, o.alert as descrCodiceIstatPrinc, o.codice3 as codiceIstatSec3,o.codice2 as codiceIstatSec2,o.codice1 as codiceIstatSec1,o.codice4 as codiceIstatSec4,o.codice5 as codiceIstatSec5,o.codice6 as codiceIstatSec6,o.codice7 as codiceIstatSec7,o.codice8 as codiceIstatSec8,o.codice9 as codiceIstatSec9,o.codice10 as codiceIstatSec10, o.cab as descrCodiceIstatSec, o.conto_corrente as tipoAutoveicolo, o.nome_correntista as targaAutoveicolo, o.duns_type as tipoDia, o.date1 as dataDia, o.date2 as dataInizioAttivita, o.contract_end as dataFineAttivita, o.year_started as livelloRischio, cod1.short_description AS descr1,cod2.short_description AS descr2,cod3.short_description AS descr3,cod4.short_description AS descr4,cod5.short_description AS descr5,cod6.short_description AS descr6,cod7.short_description AS descr7, o.notes as note,o.tipo_dest as attivita, lookup_site_id.description as asl, lookup_contact_source.description as carattere, lookup_contact_types.description as tipologiaContatto, lookup_org_catrischio.description as categoriaOsa, lookup_requestor_stage.description as tipologiaDIA, oaleg.addrline1 as indirizzolegale, oaleg.postalcode as caplegale, oaleg.city as cittalegale, oaleg.state as provincialegale, oaleg.longitude as longitudinelegale, oaleg.latitude as latitudinelegale, oaope.addrline1 as indirizzooperativo, oaope.postalcode as capoperativo, oaope.city as cittaoperativo, oaope.state as provinciaoperativo, oaope.longitude as longitudineoperativo, oaope.latitude as latitudineoperativo, mobile.addrline1 as indirizzomobile, mobile.postalcode as capmobile, mobile.city as cittamobile, mobile.state as provinciamobile, mobile.longitude as longitudinemobile, mobile.latitude as latitudinemobile, o.email_rappresentante as emailrappr, o.telefono_rappresentante as telrappr,o.codice_fiscale_rappresentante as cfrappr, oaloc.addrline1 as indirizzolocale, CURRENT_TIMESTAMP as dataoggi, oaloc.postalcode as caplocale, oaloc.city as cittalocale, oaloc.state as provincialocale, oaloc.longitude as longitudinelocale, oaloc.latitude as latitudinelocale, op.extension as prefissoTelefono, op.number as numeroTelefono, o.data_in_carattere AS tempDA,o.data_fine_carattere AS tempA, oe.email as email, cont.namesalutation as titoloProprietario, cont.namelast as nomeProprietario, o.tipologia as tipologia, o.cognome_rappresentante || ' ' || o.nome_rappresentante as rappresentante FROM organization o LEFT JOIN lookup_site_id ON (o.site_id = lookup_site_id.code) LEFT JOIN lookup_contact_source ON (o.source = lookup_contact_source.code) LEFT JOIN lookup_org_catrischio ON (o.account_size = lookup_org_catrischio.code) LEFT JOIN lookup_requestor_stage ON (o.stage_id = lookup_requestor_stage.code) LEFT JOIN organization_address oaleg ON (o.org_id = oaleg.org_id and oaleg.address_type = 1) LEFT JOIN organization_address oaope ON (o.org_id = oaope.org_id and oaope.address_type = 5) LEFT JOIN organization_address oaloc ON (o.org_id = oaloc.org_id and oaloc.address_type = 6) LEFT JOIN organization_address mobile ON (o.org_id = mobile.org_id and mobile.address_type = 7) LEFT JOIN organization_phone op ON (o.org_id = op.org_id) LEFT JOIN organization_emailaddress oe ON (o.org_id = oe.org_id)
LEFT JOIN lookup_codistat cod1 ON (cod1.description = o.codice1) LEFT JOIN lookup_codistat cod2 ON (cod2.description = o.codice2) LEFT JOIN lookup_codistat cod3 ON (cod3.description = o.codice3) LEFT JOIN lookup_codistat cod4 ON (cod4.description = o.codice4) LEFT JOIN lookup_codistat cod5 ON (cod5.description = o.codice5) LEFT JOIN lookup_codistat cod6 ON (cod6.description = o.codice6) LEFT JOIN lookup_codistat cod7 ON (cod7.description = o.codice7) LEFT JOIN contact cont LEFT JOIN contact_type_levels ctl LEFT JOIN lookup_contact_types ON (lookup_contact_types.code = ctl.type_id) ON (ctl.contact_id = cont.contact_id) ON (o.org_id = cont.org_id)
WHERE o.org_id = $P{orgid} AND o.trashed_date IS NULL
